{"id":254,"ayahs":[{"number":35,"arabic":"۞ مَّثَلُ ٱلْجَنَّةِ ٱلَّتِى وُعِدَ ٱلْمُتَّقُونَ ۖ تَجْرِى مِن تَحْتِهَا ٱلْأَنْهَٰرُ ۖ أُكُلُهَا دَآئِمٌۭ وَظِلُّهَا ۚ تِلْكَ عُقْبَى ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّقَوا۟ ۖ وَّعُقْبَى ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ ٱلنَّارُ","translation":"THE PARABLE of the paradise promised to those who are conscious of God [is that of a garden] through which running waters flow: [but, unlike an earthly garden,] its fruits will be everlasting, and [so will be] its shade. Such will be the destiny of those who remain conscious of God-just as the destiny of those who deny the truth will be the fire.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1742.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":37539,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ مَّثَلُ","translation":"দৃষ্টান্ত (পরিচয়)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37540,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","translation":"জান্নাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37541,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37542,"position":4,"arabic":"وُعِدَ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি দেয়া হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37543,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَّقُونَ ۖ","translation":"মুত্তাকীদের (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37545,"position":6,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","translation":"প্রবাহিত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37546,"position":7,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37547,"position":8,"arabic":"تَحْتِهَا","translation":"তার নিচ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37548,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ ۖ","translation":"ঝর্ণাসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37550,"position":10,"arabic":"أُكُلُهَا","translation":"তার ফলসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37551,"position":11,"arabic":"دَآئِمٌۭ","translation":"চিরস্হায়ী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37552,"position":12,"arabic":"وَظِلُّهَا ۚ","translation":"এবং তার ছায়াও (অবিনশ্বর)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37554,"position":13,"arabic":"تِلْكَ","translation":"এসব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37555,"position":14,"arabic":"عُقْبَى","translation":"পরিণাম","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37556,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37557,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱتَّقَوا۟ ۖ","translation":"(আল্লাহকে) ভয় করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37559,"position":17,"arabic":"وَّعُقْبَى","translation":"ও পরিণাম","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37560,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"কাফেরদের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37561,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارُ","translation":"(জাহান্নামের) আগুন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_035_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":37562,"position":20,"arabic":"٣٥","translation":"(৩৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":36,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَاتَيْنَٰهُمُ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ يَفْرَحُونَ بِمَآ أُنزِلَ إِلَيْكَ ۖ وَمِنَ ٱلْأَحْزَابِ مَن يُنكِرُ بَعْضَهُۥ ۚ قُلْ إِنَّمَآ أُمِرْتُ أَنْ أَعْبُدَ ٱللَّهَ وَلَآ أُشْرِكَ بِهِۦٓ ۚ إِلَيْهِ أَدْعُوا۟ وَإِلَيْهِ مَـَٔابِ","translation":"Hence, they unto whom We have vouchsafed this revelation rejoice at all that has been bestowed upon thee [O Prophet] from on high; but among the followers of other creeds there are such as deny the validity of some of it. Say [unto them, O Prophet]: \"I have only been bidden to worship God, and not to ascribe divine. powers to aught beside Him: unto Him do I call [all mankind], and He is my goal!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1743.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":38420,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"এবং যাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38421,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَاتَيْنَـٰهُمُ","translation":"আমরা দিয়েছি তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38422,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ","translation":"কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38423,"position":4,"arabic":"يَفْرَحُونَ","translation":"তারা আনন্দ পায়","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38424,"position":5,"arabic":"بِمَآ","translation":"এ কারণে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38425,"position":6,"arabic":"أُنزِلَ","translation":"অবতরণ করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38426,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَيْكَ ۖ","translation":"তোমার প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38428,"position":8,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","translation":"আবার কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38429,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَحْزَابِ","translation":"বিভিন্ন দলের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38430,"position":10,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"কেউ কেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38431,"position":11,"arabic":"يُنكِرُ","translation":"অস্বীকার করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38432,"position":12,"arabic":"بَعْضَهُۥ ۚ","translation":"তার কিছু অংশ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38434,"position":13,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38435,"position":14,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","translation":"\"শুধুমাত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38436,"position":15,"arabic":"أُمِرْتُ","translation":"আমাকে আদেশ করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38437,"position":16,"arabic":"أَنْ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38438,"position":17,"arabic":"أَعْبُدَ","translation":"আমি (যেন) ইবাদত করি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38439,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38440,"position":19,"arabic":"وَلَآ","translation":"এবং না (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38441,"position":20,"arabic":"أُشْرِكَ","translation":"আমি শরীক করি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38442,"position":21,"arabic":"بِهِۦٓ ۚ","translation":"তাঁর সাথে (অন্য কাউকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38444,"position":22,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","translation":"তাঁরই দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38445,"position":23,"arabic":"أَدْعُوا۟","translation":"আমি ডাকি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38446,"position":24,"arabic":"وَإِلَيْهِ","translation":"ও তাঁরই দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38447,"position":25,"arabic":"مَـَٔابِ","translation":"আমার গন্তব্যস্থান\"","audioUrl":"wbw/013_036_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38448,"position":26,"arabic":"٣٦","translation":"(৩৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":37,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ أَنزَلْنَٰهُ حُكْمًا عَرَبِيًّۭا ۚ وَلَئِنِ ٱتَّبَعْتَ أَهْوَآءَهُم بَعْدَمَا جَآءَكَ مِنَ ٱلْعِلْمِ مَا لَكَ مِنَ ٱللَّهِ مِن وَلِىٍّۢ وَلَا وَاقٍۢ","translation":"Thus, then, have We bestowed from on high this [divine writ] as an ordinance in the Arabic tongue. And, indeed, if thou shouldst defer to men's likes and dislikes after all the [divine] knowledge that has come unto thee, thou wouldst have none to protect thee from God, and none to shield thee [from Him].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1744.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":39271,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এবং এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39272,"position":2,"arabic":"أَنزَلْنَـٰهُ","translation":"তা আমরা অবতীর্ণ করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39273,"position":3,"arabic":"حُكْمًا","translation":"বিধানরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39274,"position":4,"arabic":"عَرَبِيًّۭا ۚ","translation":"আরবী ভাষায়","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39276,"position":5,"arabic":"وَلَئِنِ","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39277,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱتَّبَعْتَ","translation":"তুমি অনুসরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39278,"position":7,"arabic":"أَهْوَآءَهُم","translation":"তাদের খেয়ালখুশীর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39279,"position":8,"arabic":"بَعْدَ مَا","translation":"পরেও যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39280,"position":9,"arabic":"جَآءَكَ","translation":"তোমার কাছে এসেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39281,"position":10,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39282,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْعِلْمِ","translation":"জ্ঞান","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39283,"position":12,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39284,"position":13,"arabic":"لَكَ","translation":"তোমার জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39285,"position":14,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"বিরুদ্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39286,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39287,"position":16,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39288,"position":17,"arabic":"وَلِىٍّۢ","translation":"অভিভাবক (বাঁচাতে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39289,"position":18,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39290,"position":19,"arabic":"وَاقٍۢ","translation":"কোনো রক্ষাকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_037_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39291,"position":20,"arabic":"٣٧","translation":"(৩৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":38,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ أَرْسَلْنَا رُسُلًۭا مِّن قَبْلِكَ وَجَعَلْنَا لَهُمْ أَزْوَٰجًۭا وَذُرِّيَّةًۭ ۚ وَمَا كَانَ لِرَسُولٍ أَن يَأْتِىَ بِـَٔايَةٍ إِلَّا بِإِذْنِ ٱللَّهِ ۗ لِكُلِّ أَجَلٍۢ كِتَابٌۭ","translation":"And, truly, We sent forth apostles before thee, and We appointed for them wives and offspring; and it was not given to any apostle to produce a miracle save at God's behest. Every age has had its revelation:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1745.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":40100,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40101,"position":2,"arabic":"أَرْسَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা প্রেরণ করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40102,"position":3,"arabic":"رُسُلًۭا","translation":"রাসূলদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40103,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"থেকেই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40104,"position":5,"arabic":"قَبْلِكَ","translation":"তোমার পূর্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40105,"position":6,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা দিয়েছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40106,"position":7,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40107,"position":8,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجًۭا","translation":"স্ত্রীসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40108,"position":9,"arabic":"وَذُرِّيَّةًۭ ۚ","translation":"ও সন্তান-সন্ততি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40110,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40111,"position":11,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিলো (সম্ভব)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40112,"position":12,"arabic":"لِرَسُولٍ","translation":"কোনো রাসূলের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40113,"position":13,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40114,"position":14,"arabic":"يَأْتِىَ","translation":"সে আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40115,"position":15,"arabic":"بِـَٔايَةٍ","translation":"নিয়ে কোনো নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40116,"position":16,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40117,"position":17,"arabic":"بِإِذْنِ","translation":"নিয়ে অনুমতি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40118,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۗ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40120,"position":19,"arabic":"لِكُلِّ","translation":"জন্যে প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40121,"position":20,"arabic":"أَجَلٍۢ","translation":"নির্ধারিত যুগের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40122,"position":21,"arabic":"كِتَابٌۭ","translation":"একটি কিতাব (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_038_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40123,"position":22,"arabic":"٣٨","translation":"(৩৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":39,"arabic":"يَمْحُوا۟ ٱللَّهُ مَا يَشَآءُ وَيُثْبِتُ ۖ وَعِندَهُۥٓ أُمُّ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ","translation":"God annuls or confirms whatever He wills [of His earlier messages] -for with Him is the source of all revelation.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1746.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":40870,"position":1,"arabic":"يَمْحُوا۟","translation":"নিশ্চিহ্ন করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40871,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40872,"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40873,"position":4,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ","translation":"ইচ্ছে করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40874,"position":5,"arabic":"وَيُثْبِتُ ۖ","translation":"ও বহাল রাখেন (যা চান)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40876,"position":6,"arabic":"وَعِندَهُۥٓ","translation":"এবং তাঁর কাছে আছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40877,"position":7,"arabic":"أُمُّ","translation":"মূল","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40878,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাবের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_039_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40879,"position":9,"arabic":"٣٩","translation":"(৩৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":40,"arabic":"وَإِن مَّا نُرِيَنَّكَ بَعْضَ ٱلَّذِى نَعِدُهُمْ أَوْ نَتَوَفَّيَنَّكَ فَإِنَّمَا عَلَيْكَ ٱلْبَلَٰغُ وَعَلَيْنَا ٱلْحِسَابُ","translation":"BUT WHETHER We let thee see [in thy lifetime, O Prophet, the fulfilment of] some of what We have promised them, or whether We cause thee to die [before its fulfilment] - thy duty is no more than to deliver the message; and the reckoning is Ours.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1747.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":41762,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41763,"position":2,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41764,"position":3,"arabic":"نُرِيَنَّكَ","translation":"তোমাকে আমরা দেখাই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41765,"position":4,"arabic":"بَعْضَ","translation":"কিছুটা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41766,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41767,"position":6,"arabic":"نَعِدُهُمْ","translation":"তাদের প্রতিশ্রুতি দিচ্ছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41768,"position":7,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41769,"position":8,"arabic":"نَتَوَفَّيَنَّكَ","translation":"তোমাকে মৃত্যু দিই আমরা (যাই হউক)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41770,"position":9,"arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا","translation":"প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41771,"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَيْكَ","translation":"তোমার দায়িত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41772,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْبَلَـٰغُ","translation":"প্রচার করা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41773,"position":12,"arabic":"وَعَلَيْنَا","translation":"এবং আমাদের দায়িত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41774,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْحِسَابُ","translation":"হিসাব-নিকাশের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_040_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41775,"position":14,"arabic":"٤٠","translation":"(৪০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":41,"arabic":"أَوَلَمْ يَرَوْا۟ أَنَّا نَأْتِى ٱلْأَرْضَ نَنقُصُهَا مِنْ أَطْرَافِهَا ۚ وَٱللَّهُ يَحْكُمُ لَا مُعَقِّبَ لِحُكْمِهِۦ ۚ وَهُوَ سَرِيعُ ٱلْحِسَابِ","translation":"Have, then, they [who deny the truth] never yet seen how We visit the earth [with Our punishment], gradually depriving it of all that is best thereon? For, [when] God judges, there is no power that could repel His judgment: and swift in reckoning is He!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1748.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":42533,"position":1,"arabic":"أَوَلَمْ","translation":"কি নি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42534,"position":2,"arabic":"يَرَوْا۟","translation":"তারা দেখে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42535,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّا","translation":"যে আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42536,"position":4,"arabic":"نَأْتِى","translation":"আমরা চলে আসছি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42537,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"জমিনের (উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42538,"position":6,"arabic":"نَنقُصُهَا","translation":"তা সংকুচিত করছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42539,"position":7,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42540,"position":8,"arabic":"أَطْرَافِهَا ۚ","translation":"তার চারপাশ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42542,"position":9,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42543,"position":10,"arabic":"يَحْكُمُ","translation":"আদেশ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42544,"position":11,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42545,"position":12,"arabic":"مُعَقِّبَ","translation":"কোনো প্রতিহতকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42546,"position":13,"arabic":"لِحُكْمِهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তাঁর আদেশের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_041_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42548,"position":14,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/01